metadata.name: LAC Holiday Sparks Airdrop by GLR
metadata.description:
For all the holders of the pieces from the Holiday Sparks Collection. You've received the official gift of yule tide cheer for all the friends that we have made along the way. Thank you all for being such a great part of the growth, and wholesomeness that is LAC.

This is a limited-edition piece from a great artist known as GLR.  
Please check out his work, and progress?

https://twitter.com/glennleerob

Happy Holidays to you all.

Peace & Love,  
LAC

https://twitter.com/LostArtistCo
